{"tid":657004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果知道自己幾時死啲話係咪先會珍惜眼前所有","createTime":"2018-05-07T17:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T18:36:42.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a19613ca94feab49fca509b98dc6604456a63680","tid":657004,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"有人同我講過<br />\n連死都唔驚，仲有咩好驚<br />\n已經俾身邊好多人屌我成日郁啲就逃避<br />\n唔敢嘗試，怕失敗<br />\n但都仲係好迷茫<br />\n點解人哋得自己唔得<br />\n不斷搵藉口俾自己<br />\n<br />\n有冇人明"},{"pid":"62c25bf328b009d87177a3152df3ce8bd3ff0c4e","tid":657004,"uid":103212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a4971587813c1a52439fcd8115a2e3d7ae46a31","tid":657004,"uid":51165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"肯試就有機會 唔肯試就一定無機會<br />\n唔係珍惜唔珍惜嘅問題<br />\n雖然唔知你講緊邊方面嘅煩惱<br />\n但人地成功一定係因為人地有努力，唔係個個都會努力俾人睇，只係人地努力緊嘅時候你唔知啫"},{"pid":"d7d7c197312e3e76723c24846bf85c805b0d9fea","tid":657004,"uid":51165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"盡咗力而失敗 喺人地眼中<br />\n點都好過逃避而一事無成<br />\n無錯係唔會失敗 但只係顯得你怕事 仲衰過失敗"},{"pid":"1cd041f35e63f437cdef8841db4db79e1ce1385e","tid":657004,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31f1ec54c2905a15252820201db12177f54dc741","tid":657004,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"姦淫擄掠<br />\n慾望最大化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e00b767e4c561c92072695ed73888afd4bd9969","tid":657004,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c25bf328b009d87177a3152df3ce8bd3ff0c4e","tid":657004,"uid":103212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"我做錯好多嘢<br />\n返唔到轉頭<br />\n晒咗好多錢同時間去讀書<br />\n結果除咗